item.title: What am I doing wrong?
item.description: Oftentimes, I find myself desperate for attention, hoping that anyone would notice me.As I recall in my childhood, I’ve been pleasing people most of my life. I will literally do anything in my power not to disappoint anyone. Whether it’s some person that wants their laptop check, or helping with their coding problems, I will go to your place. Not the opposite. I know, that really sucks but it is what it is.
